24 years ago...

70
00:10:03,489 --> 00:10:05,405
I was practicing law in Lucknow.

71
00:10:05,485 --> 00:10:10,62
I was the black sheep of the family,
because I opposed social norm...

72
00:10:10,564 --> 00:10:14,342
